Package it.unica.foresee.datasets.interfaces

Interface Summary
ClonableElement<T> Wrapper to create clonable elements.
Dataset<T extends DatasetElement> Represents a generic dataset.
DatasetElement<T> Represents an element from a dataset.
DatasetLoader<T extends Dataset> Generic interface to load a Dataset.
DatasetNestedSparseVector<T extends DatasetSparseVector<?>> Defines Sparse Vectors of Sparse Vectors.
DatasetVector<T extends DatasetElement> Vector of data.
DeepClonable<T> Element that can be deep cloned.
DoubleConvertible<T> An element that can be converted to double.
FileDatasetLoader<T extends Dataset> Loads datasets from files.
Identifiable Element that can be identified.
NumberElement<T extends Number> An element containing a number.
SolutionElement<T> Represents the solution or output of a certain function.
